messages.message:
as discussed during Frontend Guild, i removed the shift/merge/collapse/collapseBoard starter code from the interview template! i used the new template in an interview and confirmed that the deleted starter code no longer appears

the interview guide (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1D94bVSBs28ve7XuFfI4dqAs50VspbXhAVUIVBOl1ooM/edit?tab=t.0) already provides the same deleted code to copy-paste into the editor when the candidate gets to part 4
